FBIS3-531 "drafr046_c_94027" FBIS-AFR-94-046 Document Type:Daily Report 9 Mar 1994 REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA Abolishes Detention Without Trial MB0903085794 Johannesburg SABC TV 1 Network in English 0500 GMT 9 Mar 94 MB0903085794 Johannesburg SABC TV 1 Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] The Transitional Executive Council [TEC] has decided to scrap detention without trial. The TEC also agreed that all existing legislation be reviewed to see whether it catered adequately for the current security situation.
